				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/B%C3%ACnh-san-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87p-thu%C3%BD/poem--2GrNK0Qo7XTgEid3Or3oA">Bình san điệp thuý - 屏山疊翠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/author-GLzqIGvVnoBURna-hgD_jw">Mạc Thiên Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-L%E1%BB%8Bch-tam-ni%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-th%C3%A0nh-ph%C3%B3ng-thuy%E1%BB%81n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-C%C3%B9-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-gi%C3%A1p-c%E1%BB%ADu-c%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch/poem-FdJ4yvYyTSKfMStGhGDgGg">Đại Lịch tam niên xuân Bạch Đế thành phóng thuyền xuất Cù Đường giáp, cửu cư Quỳ Phủ tương thích Giang Lăng phiêu bạc, hữu thi phàm tứ thập vận - 大歷三年春白帝城放船出瞿唐峽久居夔府將適江陵漂泊有詩凡四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BB%87-xu%C3%A2n/poem-B4WQD1gwOE-F5G7NQjsUXQ">Lệ xuân - 麗春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/Ly-tao/poem-kvKLhIt8jjW5-ExLsxl1UQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/author-FCMLXx_iJwv1UkwFEUT-cw">Lục Quy Mông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ng%C6%B0-ly-2/poem-5bfRtrFe1QWfJD_i5rVpzA">Ngư ly 2 - 魚麗 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Anh-t%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-LPHmWUli34MRI5ziIHDrUw">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Anh tài tử” - 奉和御製英才子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-d6YU4KPKjTplShZhxLPIUg">Vũ Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C3%A2n-thu-ng%E1%BA%ABu-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Tân thu ngẫu hứng - 新秋偶興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93/poem-0HE9KmVtI6MzgnIFqADRwg">Tây Hồ - 西湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%BAc-Do%C3%A3n-Minh/Th%C3%A1i-H%C3%A0ng-ca/poem-JdVKbgfQXI9UwOiTt522sA">Thái Hàng ca - 太行歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%BAc-Do%C3%A3n-Minh/author-e4jgq1mPvB3W96Qec2yOQg">Chúc Doãn Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Giai/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-c%C3%B4ng-chi-%C4%90oan-H%C3%B9ng/poem-VEWFzIoIrYX9-wuAdMH53w">Tiễn Phạm công chi Đoan Hùng - 餞范公之端雄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Giai/author-tbVETc5SFc0ZkdKBtLYjiw">Nguyễn Công Giai</a>)<br></div>	</div>
